Web Demo on Docker

Base images:
busybox
tomcat
nginx


Front:
nginx docker instance => 8081
Backend:
1 mockserver docker instance
2 tomcatserver docker instances (vue sample)


URI:
# helloworld
http://helloworld.zj.com:8081
http://helloworld.zj.com:8081/public/helloworld.html
http://helloworld.zj.com:8081/static/pics/1.jpg

# mockserver
http://mockserver.zj.com:8081/images/1.jpg (static => not found)
http://mockserver.zj.com:8081/index?isFile=false&wait=1
http://mockserver.zj.com:8081/test1?userid=xxx&username=%22xxx%22&url=url1&url=url2
http://mockserver.zj.com:8081/post/cdnrefresh

# vueserver
http://vueserver.zj.com:8081
http://vueserver.zj.com:8081/static/index.html
http://vueserver.zj.com:8081/vueapp


CLI:
$ docker-compose -p zjwebgroup up -d --scale tomcatserver=2
$ docker-compose -p zjwebgroup down

